Personal Banking

            At Valley National Bank we want to exceed your expectations. We provide the products and services you want the way you want them, whether it's in person, on the telephone or via the Internet. This "high touch, high service" approach makes Valley one of the most successful banks in the industry. If you are looking for a Checking or Savings Account, Home Mortgage or Online Banking, Valley's Personal Accounts section will have what's right for you.
         

